text: Madeleine Bochatay (born 2 January 1944) is a French alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:People from Saint- Gervais, Isère Category:French female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of France Category:Alpine skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Isère
